column1: # Name: Share employed in industry, Male
# Definition: Share of males in industry. Employment is disaggregated into three broad sectors – agriculture, industry and services – and expresses each as a percentage of total employment.
# Source: International Labour Organization (ILO) Key Indicators of the Labour Market (KILM)
# Data from the No Ceilings project: http://noceilings.org
# For more about the data, please visit http://noceilings.org/data
